          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJPWUxY97QBICOPfqpWKu5cKlaMrscVkfZ82ni2KVXdJmwp6w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "HSS PT is an all around great place. Everyone I\u2019ve met is warm, concerned and helpful. The facility is attractive and extensive- there is a large well equipped gym as well as private rooms. Although I have had pt several times in the past, this is the first time where I have had such a thorough assessment prior to the establishment of a treatment plan. Each session has ended with exercises to do at home, which are relevant and can be accomplished without equipment. I highly recommend them.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2w5bmVFRllaRVk0VWtJeU0wMVBRelJzU21GVldXYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xe664ef702671d9b!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOl9neEFYZEY4UkIyM01PQzRsSmFVWWc%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "Edited 4 months ago",
          "date_iso8601": "2026-02-17T16:19:15+00:00"
