          "description": "The Physical Therapists are great! The office staff - HORRIBLE.\nSome of the rudest scheduling staff I've ever delt with. Trying to make an appointment here is nearly impossible, they schedule weeks out in advance and when i called to reschedule 1 appt (the only one i have ever needed too) they just canceled it and told me nothing else was available for the rest of the year?????? I find that very hard to believe.",
