          "description": "Joyce my massage therapist and Kyle my PT are truly healers. They know how to listen to patient in this critical recovery from an injury and surgery\nThanks for helping me to be whole again!\n20 starts\n\n6/9/26  addition to previous review\nOne start for HSS customer care, they offered only 30 mts PT. Insurance is charge as a hospital visit. I had to pay additional co payments. I had to leave this place. They are not transparent . Therapists are ok but not enough time to provide quality care.",
